snippet.title: Mario Odyssey Reimagined for the N64! (Release and Download)
snippet.description:
Lots moons to collect! 80 in Total.
For more fangames, subscribe!: https://www.youtube.com/c/KazeEmanuar?sub_confirmation=1
Demos, funding: https://www.patreon.com/Kazestuff
I do livestreams!: https://www.twitch.tv/kazesm64

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HyCX8kcyIns

Patch the downloaded file on your Super Mario 64 US.z64 rom!
